<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> التَّنْبِيهُ عَلَى قَولِهِ: ﴿أَلَا إِنَّمَا طَائِرُهُمْ عِنْدَ اللَّهِ﴾ مَعَ قَولِهِ: ﴿طَائِرُكُمْ مَعَكُمْ﴾.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> نَفْيُ العَدْوَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> نَفْيُ الطِّيَرَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> نَفْيُ الهَامَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> نَفْيُ الصَّفَرِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسَةُ:</span> أَنَّ الفَأْلَ لَيسَ مِنْ ذَلِكَ؛ بَلْ مُسْتَحَبٌّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعَةُ:</span> تَفْسِيرُ الفَأْلِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الثَّامِنَةُ:</span> أَنَّ الوَاقِعَ فِي القُلُوبِ مِنْ ذَلِكَ مَعَ كَرَاهَتِهِ؛ لَا يَضُرُّ بَلْ يُذْهِبُهُ اللهُ بِالتَّوَكُّلِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">التَّاسِعَةُ:</span> ذِكْرُ مَا يَقُولُ مَنْ وَجَدَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">العَاشِرَةُ:</span> التَّصْرِيحُ بِأَنَّ الطِّيَرَةَ شِرْكٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">الحَادِيَةَ عَشْرَةَ:</span> تَفْسِيرُ الطِّيَرَةِ المَذْمُومَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>